*Drugog* puta je razmišljao o tome. (He thought about it a second time.)

*Drugog* dana smo došli do odredišta. (We reached our destination on the second day.)

*Drugom* nastavniku je ovo bilo veoma interesantno. (The second teacher found this very interesting.)

*Drugoga* će verovatno morati da zamoli za pomoć. (He will probably have to ask someone else for help.)

*Drugog* je čoveka iznenadila ta vest. (The news surprised the second man.)

*Drugom* nam je bilo teško da postignemo dogovor. (It was difficult for us to reach an agreement the second time.)